Record notable learnings in `.opencode/learnings/`.

## Filename

`{date}-(package:{pkg})-({title})-(tags:{tags}).md`

## Content

```markdown
---
date: yyyy-mm-dd
package: core
tags: [tag1, tag2]
---

# {Title}

{One or two sentences. No more.}
```

## When to Record

Record project-specific insights (not general knowledge), mistakes to avoid, and patterns that worked.
